## Workflow
- Use `/forge` for features (3+ files) — automated pipeline with review
- Use `/forge --full` for complex tasks — adds deliberation + parallel execution
- Use `/git-save` when ready to commit
- Use `/overseer` for pre-merge code review
- Use `/slop-scan` to detect tech debt

## What NOT to do
- Don't add features beyond what was asked
- Don't refactor code you didn't change
- Don't add comments to self-explanatory code
- Don't commit .env files or secrets
